TALK Narrator To pick up an item, simply walk into it. Any collectable items will be added to your inventory.
TALK Narrator You can view the contents of your inventory by pressing [INPUT_INVENTORY]
TALK Narrator Whilst in the inventory, use the arrow keys to view the items.
TALK Narrator You can use an item immediately by pressing Attack ([INPUT_ATTACK]) or Use Item ([INPUT_ACTIVATE])
TALK Narrator You can ready an item for use by pressing Block ([INPUT_BLOCK]) or Action ([INPUT_INTERACT])
TALK Narrator You can also sort items in your inventory by using the Previous Item ([INPUT_PREVIOUS]) and Next Item ([INPUT_NEXT]) buttons
